# Runtime knowledge wiki (LLM-maintained output). Gitignored so it persists across
# `git reset --hard` redeploys and never leaks listing data into the repo. The governing
# WIKI_SCHEMA.md *is* tracked. Override the location with WIKI_DIR.
# Anchored to the repo root so it never matches the source package src/apartment_agent/wiki/.
/wiki/

# Only the sanitized sample fixture is tracked; never commit raw scraped captures
tests/fixtures/*
!tests/fixtures/wg_sample.html

